    VarLenBulkEntry
    A bulk input entry enables us to process potentially multiple VL values in one shot (especially for very small values); please refer to org.apache.drill.exec.vector.VarBinaryVector.BulkInput.
    VarLenBulkInput<T extends VarLenBulkEntry>
    Allows caller to provide input in a bulk manner while abstracting the underlying data structure to provide performance optimizations opportunities.
    VarLenBulkInput.BulkInputCallback<T extends VarLenBulkEntry>
    Enables caller (such as wrapper vector objects) to include more processing logic as the data is being streamed.

    VectorOverflowException
